The paper presents a test platform for visual in-cabin scene analysis and occupant monitoring functions, which involves computer vision, human-computer interaction, robotics, artificial intelligence, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
